content.raw:
How about we at least try to make sure Ubuntu is working on Pipelines and Jenkins before merging this? I updated pipelines to use `ign-common3` on 914aa07 and [this PR](https://bitbucket.org/osrf/release-tools/pull-requests/714) should fix the Jenkins build.

My reasoning is that this pull request is bumping dependencies without even the need to use them, so the least we could do is take the opportunity to bump CI as well.
content.html:
How about we at least try to make sure Ubuntu is working on Pipelines and Jenkins before merging this? I updated pipelines to use ign-common3 on 914aa07 and this PR should fix the Jenkins build.

My reasoning is that this pull request is bumping dependencies without even the need to use them, so the least we could do is take the opportunity to bump CI as well.
